column4:
['Kis taraf ko dhyan hai tera', '
Oo dile nadan, oo dile nadan', '
Oo dile nadan', '
Palat tera dhyan kidhar hai bhayi', '
Varna pachhtana padega', '
Main tere kurban, main tere kurban', '
Main tere kurban palat,', '
Arey palat tera dhyan kidhar hai', '
Dillagi samjhi hai tune', '
Dil lagana mein', '
Koi dil lagana mein koi', '
Arey aisa mushkil hai nahi ye', '
Ye kam kuchh aasan', '
Ye kam kuchh asan', '
Arey kam kuchh asan', '
Palat tera dhyan kidhar hai bhayi', 'Jhopado mein rahne wale', '
Khawab mahalo ke na dekh', '
Khawab mahalo ke na dekh', '
Arey in kitabire hai teri', 'Arey mot ka saman', '
Aye mot ka saman', '
Oo mot ka saman palat', '
Palat tera dhyan', '
Kidhar hai bhayi', 'Kah raha hoon pas aaja', '
Dekh dhokha khayega', '
Aa dekh dhokha khayega', '
Dil mein hi rahne de apne', 'Yeh dil ke ye arma dil ke ye arma', '
Dil ke ye arma palat palat', '
Arey palat tera dhyan', '
Kidhar hai bhayi.']
